text:
🏋️The padded floor Fitness Corner lies at the south edge of the neighborhood park.
🧗Residents can access to workout anytime of the day.
🏃Sitting next to the Fitness Corner is a space delicated to IPPT (Individual Physical Proficiency Test) Standing Broad Jump cum Shuttle Run Station complete with an Info Board detailing it's scores.
🏃NS men can do pre-test trials here to gauge their proficiency.
